OL,3,CMan who stopped drivers during riot to
OL,4,Ccheck if they were 'white' jailed
OL,6,FA man who stopped drivers in
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough to check if they were
OL,8,F"white" or "English" during the summer
OL,9,Friots has been jailed.
OL,11,FJake Wray, 23, of Seaton Street,
OL,12,FMiddlesbrough, was sentenced to three
OL,13,Fyears and two months in prison after
OL,14,Fadmitting violent disorder in the town
OL,15,Fon August 4, including trying to set a
OL,16,Fcar on fire, making racist chants and
OL,17,Fpushing flaming wheelie bins into
OL,18,Fpolice lines.
