OL,3,CMan who stopped drivers during riot to
OL,4,Ccheck if they were 'white' jailed
OL,6,FHe was serving a 24-week suspended
OL,7,Fsentence for spitting at a police
OL,8,Fofficer and carrying a knife at the
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FJudge Richard Bennett, sentencing at
OL,12,FTeesside Crown Court, told Wray:
OL,13,F"(Your) behaviour was disgraceful and
OL,14,Fin no way reflects the values of the
OL,15,Fdecent people of Middlesbrough."
OL,17,FThe judge said Wray's offending was
OL,18,Fviolent, "overtly racist" and included
OL,19,Farson that day.
