OL,3,CMan who stopped drivers during riot to
OL,4,Ccheck if they were 'white' jailed
OL,6,FWray, wearing a distinctive red top
OL,7,Fand an England flag around his
OL,8,Fshoulders, stopped cars at a junction
OL,9,Fin the town centre and was caught on
OL,10,Fmobile phone footage asking drivers
OL,11,Fabout the colour of their skin.
OL,13,FOn the clip which was played in court,
OL,14,Fwhile he stood blocking traffic, Wray
OL,15,Fcould be heard asking: "Are you white,
OL,16,Fare you English?"
OL,18,FThe judge said the incident was so
OL,19,Fshocking, it was played on the
OL,20,Fnational TV news.
