OL,3,CMan who stopped drivers during riot to
OL,4,Ccheck if they were 'white' jailed
OL,6,FFurther clips showed him setting fire
OL,7,Fto a wheelie bin which was pushed
OL,8,Ftowards police lines and helicopter
OL,9,Fvideo captured him interfering with a
OL,10,Fred hatchback which minutes later
OL,11,Fburst into flames.
OL,13,FWray told police that he was merely
OL,14,Fstopping cars to warn drivers, but he
OL,15,Fno longer stood by that account.
OL,17,FJudge Bennett said: "You were clearly
OL,18,Fenjoying the attention and power of
OL,19,Fbeing masked during a frightening
OL,20,Fevent for those drivers."
