OL,3,CMan who stopped drivers during riot to
OL,4,Ccheck if they were 'white' jailed
OL,6,FA clip was played in court of Wray,
OL,7,Fwith his England flag over his mouth
OL,8,Fas a mask, approaching a police video
OL,9,Foperator and shouting.
OL,11,FHarry Crowson, defending, said Wray
OL,12,Finitially denied the racial motive for
OL,13,Fstopping the cars "out of
OL,14,Fembarrassment and shame".
OL,16,FMr Crowson said the defendant had
OL,17,Frepeatedly watched the clips in court
OL,18,Fover several hearings, adding: "In the
OL,19,Fcold light of day, he doesn't even
OL,20,Fbelieve the things that came out of
OL,21,Fhis mouth that day.
